35
00:01:53,540 --> 00:01:57,420
Pronunciation of the r-colored vowel /ɚ/

36
00:01:57,420 --> 00:02:00,340
is very similar to the /ɝ/ vowel

37
00:02:00,340 --> 00:02:02,920
or the /r/ consonant.

38
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:06,760
To make the /ɚ/ sound,

39
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:10,400
open your mouth a little and leave your lips neutral

40
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,500
or round them slightly.

41
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:16,380
The /ɚ/ is a weak sound,

42
00:02:16,380 --> 00:02:19,500
