43
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:29,700
Raise the front of your tongue toward the alveolar ridge

44
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:32,520
behind your upper front teeth,

45
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:34,520
but don’t touch it.

46
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:42,500
Next: curl back the tip of your tongue.

47
00:02:42,500 --> 00:02:45,540
Now slightly lower the center of your tongue.

48
00:02:45,540 --> 00:02:48,780
and raise its back.

49
00:02:50,660 --> 00:02:53,440
Note, that your tongue should be relaxed.

